# NAME: Trading_Data
# AUTHOR: Kevin (kevshen13)
# REPO: https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# DESCRIPTION: Trading data and market data services rule list for Surge
# UPDATED: 2026-04-04
# MAINTENANCE: Maintain this list by traffic purpose and route behavior.
# RULE: Include market data feeds, quote services, historical data endpoints, and data vendor websites used for trading workflows.
# RULE: Keep broad keyword/domain rules conservative to avoid routing unrelated finance traffic.

# ==================== IQFeed / DTN ====================
DOMAIN,login.interquote.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,iqfeed.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,interquote.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dtn.com
# Official IQFeed FAQ (updated February 24, 2026) lists:
# 66.112.149.138-150 and 66.112.149.202-225 on ports 60000-60050.
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.138/31,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.140/30,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.144/30,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.148/31,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.150/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.202/31,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.204/30,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.208/28,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.112.149.224/31,no-resolve

# ==================== CQG ====================
PROCESS-NAME,CQG Integrated Client
PROCESS-NAME,CQG Trader
PROCESS-NAME,QTrader
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cqg.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cqgtrader.com
